{
  "stem": "1857.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 17.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "When it dawned on me, it was something that my imagination never-- could never form a-- a moment like that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And this is another thing that I'll never forget.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I never forget I can hear Churchill speaking.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] At that point, we took over the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And for four days, we were without the Germans and without the Russians.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But we decided that when the Russians will come and they'll get hold of Schindler, Schindler is a dead man.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So we decided that Schindler has to leave.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we gave him an escort of six people-- five men and a woman-- who went with him to protect him.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And he left with those six people in his car and a truck behind.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With his wife.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "With his wife.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Russians came in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When the moment the Russians came in, I can tell you, the liberation was not a happy one.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They walked into the camp, and the Russian officer said, you are free people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You don't have to be afraid anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Germans are defeated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Just go out and have a good time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was a Jewish soldier among the Russians who was from Vilna, which was part of Poland.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said in Yiddish, 'Don't believe what he says.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You're not free people, because they are as bad as-- as the Nazis.' [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And there was a Russian officer who-- who came into the camp and said, 'Where are you people going to go?' He said, 'They don't like you in the East, and they don't like you in the West.'",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we decided that we will go back to Krakow looking for relatives.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father had brothers and a sister.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had cousins.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
